headline: Apple (AAPL) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: Apple (AAPL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +6.94% and +1.25%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Amazon Job Cuts Broaden Big Tech’s Layoff Barrage
summary: When layoffs rise, people spend less, which leads to tighter bottom lines and more layoffs. Wash, rinse, and repeat.
